  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years with bronze skin and brown eyes set beneath heavy brows. Black hair is kept in a neat parted style, emphasizing a square jaw and a straight, well-set nose. The hands show permanent thickening at the knuckles and fingertips, consistent with long service in a working bar. A thin, healed split at the lower lip remains as a defining facial mark.",
