    "personality": "A disciplined, even-tempered bartender who runs the counter with practiced economy and an unbroken memory for faces, tabs, and preferred pours. He maintains strict boundaries, speaks plainly, and keeps disorder from spreading by reading a room faster than most patrons notice. In the Cantina’s social economy he functions as both service and informal gatekeeper, offering courtesy without familiarity and refusing intimidation as a matter of routine.",
